narrative_summary: - User requested creation of a new dbt component named `acme_dbt` pointing to the `https://github.com/dagster-io/jaffle_shop` repo
- The **dagster-expert** skill was invoked to handle the task
- Skill read reference files: `integrations/INDEX.md`, `cli/scaffold.md`, and `integrations/dagster-dbt/INDEX.md` to determine the correct approach
- Skill read `integrations/dagster-dbt/scaffolding.md` to find the remote git repo scaffold command syntax
- Scaffolded the component using `dg scaffold defs dagster_dbt.DbtProjectComponent acme_dbt --git-url https://github.com/dagster-io/jaffle_shop --project-path .`, generating `defs/acme_dbt/defs.yaml`
- Fetched the jaffle_shop `profiles.yml` via `WebFetch` to identify the dbt adapter type (DuckDB)
- Verified with `dg list defs` — all 8 dbt assets and 20 asset checks loaded successfully
